<pb n="0705a" id="T20.1171.0705a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0705a01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0705a02" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1171 [cf. No. 1175]</head>
<lb n="0705a03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0705001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等校訂加筆本，【乙】三十帖策子第十六</note>金剛頂經瑜伽文殊師利菩薩法
<lb n="0705a04" ed="T"/>一品<note n="0705002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔亦名五字&CB00057;法〕－【乙】</note><app n="0705002"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">亦名五字&CB00057;法</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0705a05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0705a06" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0705003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔開府儀同三司〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0705003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔開府儀同三司〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0705003"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同三司</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0705004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（唐）＋特【明】【甲】</note><app n="0705004"><lem wit="【大】">特</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">唐特</rdg></app>進試鴻臚<note n="0705005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔卿〕－【乙】</note><app n="0705005"><lem wit="【大】">卿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0705a07" ed="T"/><note n="0705006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔肅國…智〕二十一字－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0705006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔肅國…智〕二十一字－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app word-count="21" n="0705006"><lem wit="【大】">肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空
<lb n="0705a08" ed="T"/>謚大鑒正號大廣智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0705007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔大興善寺〕－【明】【甲】</note><app n="0705007"><lem wit="【大】">大興善寺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0705a09" ed="T"/>三藏沙<note n="0705008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">門＋（大廣智）【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0705008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門＋（大廣智）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0705008"><lem wit="【大】">門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">門大廣智</rdg></app>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0705a10" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT20p0705a1001">爾時文殊師利菩薩。在毘盧遮那大會中。從座
<lb n="0705a11" ed="T"/>而起頂禮佛足。白佛言世尊。我今說本五字
<lb n="0705a12" ed="T"/>陀羅尼。若有善男子善女人。纔誦一遍者。一
<lb n="0705a13" ed="T"/>切如來所說法<note n="0705009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">義＝藏【乙】</note><app n="0705009"><lem wit="【大】">義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">藏</rdg></app>修多羅藏。讀誦受持等彼
<lb n="0705a14" ed="T"/>功德。毘盧遮那佛。告文殊師利言。隨意說之。</p>
<lb n="0705a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0705a1501">爾時文殊師利即說。明曰。</p>
<lb n="0705a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0705a1601" type="dharani"><note n="0705010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">阿＝婀【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0705010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">阿＝婀【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0705010"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">婀</rdg></app>囉跛者曩</p>
<lb n="0705a17" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0705a1701">纔說此陀羅尼。一切如來所說<note n="0705011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（諸）&M062403;＋法【甲】</note><app n="0705011"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">諸法</rdg></app>。攝入五
<lb n="0705a18" ed="T"/>字陀羅尼中。能<note n="0705012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">令＋（利益）【宋】【元】，令＝今利益【明】</note><app n="0705012"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">令利益</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">今利益</rdg></app>眾生般若波羅蜜多成就。
<lb n="0705a19" ed="T"/>我今當說曼<note n="0705013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">荼＝茶【宋】【元】＊</note><app n="0705013"><lem wit="【大】">荼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">茶</rdg></app>羅法。或十四日十五日。選
<lb n="0705a20" ed="T"/><note n="0705014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">擇極乃至供養之四百五十字元本闕</note><note n="0705014" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>擇極乃至供養之四百五十字元本闕</note>擇極清淨處作曼<note n="0705015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">茶＝荼【明】【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0705015"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】">荼</rdg></app>羅。以瞿摩夷塗地。復
<lb n="0705a21" ed="T"/>以白檀香泥塗之。隨意大小。於曼<app source="0705013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">荼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">茶</rdg></app>羅中。
<lb n="0705a22" ed="T"/>畫文殊師<note n="0705016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">利＝別【宋】</note><app n="0705016"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">別</rdg></app><note n="0705017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔五髻〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0705017"><lem wit="【大】">五髻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>童子形狀。身如&CB00614;金色。
<lb n="0705a23" ed="T"/>種種瓔珞莊嚴其身。右手把金剛劍左手把
<lb n="0705a24" ed="T"/>梵夾。坐於月輪中。於月輪四面。周旋書五字
<lb n="0705a25" ed="T"/>陀羅尼。阿闍梨對於此壇。結金剛劍印念誦。
<lb n="0705a26" ed="T"/>時文殊師利加持此阿闍梨。即得無礙辯才。
<lb n="0705a27" ed="T"/>仍為<note n="0705018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">現＝見【乙】＊</note><app n="0705018"><lem wit="【大】">現</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">見</rdg></app>身。一一解釋此陀羅尼甚深義理。時
<lb n="0705a28" ed="T"/>阿闍梨即當禮拜出道場外。為弟子<note n="0705019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">受＝授【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0705019"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">授</rdg></app>菩薩
<lb n="0705a29" ed="T"/>戒。即以緋帛覆眼。引入壇場門次而立。時阿
<pb n="0705b" id="T20.1171.0705b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0705b01" ed="T"/>闍梨告弟子言。汝今獲一切如來般若波羅
<lb n="0705b02" ed="T"/>蜜。自今已後不應向人而說此明。勿令破汝
<lb n="0705b03" ed="T"/>三摩耶法。此陀羅尼極應祕密。<app source="0705010" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">婀</rdg></app>囉跛者曩
<lb n="0705b04" ed="T"/>者。是滿一切願義。何以故。</p>
<lb n="0705b05" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0705b0501"><app source="0705010" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">婀</rdg></app>字者樂欲菩提義。囉字者<note n="0705020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">深＝染【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0705020"><lem wit="【大】">深</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">染</rdg></app>著不捨眾
<lb n="0705b06" ed="T"/>生義。跛字者第一義諦義。者字者妙行義。曩
<lb n="0705b07" ed="T"/>字者無自性義。樂欲菩提不捨眾生。<note n="0705021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">深入＝染【宋】【乙】，染入【明】【甲】</note><note n="0705021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">深入＝染【宋】【乙】，＝染入【明】【甲】</note><app n="0705021"><lem wit="【大】">深入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【乙】">染</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">染入</rdg></app>第
<lb n="0705b08" ed="T"/>一義諦中行行。修習諸法無有自性。若如是
<lb n="0705b09" ed="T"/>修滿一切願。此諸願中證如來位及執金剛。
<lb n="0705b10" ed="T"/>不求當得。</p>
<lb n="0705b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0705b1101">我今又說<note n="0705022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">契＋（經）【宋】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0705022"><lem wit="【大】">契</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【乙】">契經</rdg></app>印曼<app source="0705015" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】">荼</rdg></app>羅。壇中畫金剛劍。四
<lb n="0705b12" ed="T"/>面各於本方。畫八供養契及四攝契。對於此
<lb n="0705b13" ed="T"/>壇念誦。不久即當成就。</p>
<lb n="0705b14" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0705b1401">我今又說三<note n="0705023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＝麼【乙】</note><app n="0705023"><lem wit="【大】">摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">麼</rdg></app>耶曼<app source="0705013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">荼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">茶</rdg></app>羅。壇中書五字及
<lb n="0705b15" ed="T"/>八供養四攝種子字。對此壇念誦而作是言。
<lb n="0705b16" ed="T"/><app source="0705010" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">婀</rdg></app>字門者諸法本不生。日日念誦。不久一切
<lb n="0705b17" ed="T"/>罪障消滅速得成就。</p>
<lb n="0705b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0705b1801">我今又說羯磨曼<app source="0705013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">荼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">茶</rdg></app>羅。壇中安般若波羅蜜
<lb n="0705b19" ed="T"/><note n="0705024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經卷＝經夾【甲】，〔經卷〕－【乙】</note><app n="0705024"><lem wit="【大】">經卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">經夾</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>。日日讀誦念誦。以種種供養而供養
<lb n="0705b20" ed="T"/>之。不久即當成就。</p>
<lb n="0705b21" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0705b2101">我今當說畫像法。或白&CB00626;絹素等中。<note n="0705025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">畫＝書【宋】【元】</note><app n="0705025"><lem wit="【大】">畫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">書</rdg></app>文殊
<lb n="0705b22" ed="T"/>師利菩薩。坐月輪中。輪內周旋書五字。四面
<lb n="0705b23" ed="T"/>畫八供養及四攝。如大壇法。對此像前如法
<lb n="0705b24" ed="T"/>念誦而作是言。諸法自性成就。念誦數滿五
<lb n="0705b25" ed="T"/>十萬遍。即獲無盡辯才。如文殊師利菩薩等
<lb n="0705b26" ed="T"/>無有異。飛騰虛空所求世間出世間事悉得
<lb n="0705b27" ed="T"/>成就。</p>
<lb n="0705b28" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0705b2801">又念誦數滿<note n="0705026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【乙】</note><app n="0705026"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>俱<note n="0705027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">胝＋（遍）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0705027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">胝＋（遍）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0705027"><lem wit="【大】">胝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">胝遍</rdg></app>。離諸苦惱。滿二俱胝
<lb n="0705b29" ed="T"/>遍。五無間等一切罪障永盡無餘。三俱胝遍。
<pb n="0705c" id="T20.1171.0705c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0705c01" ed="T"/>證悟一切諸三昧門。四俱胝遍獲大聞持。五
<lb n="0705c02" ed="T"/>俱胝遍成阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。</p>
<lb n="0705c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0705c0301">又法於舍利塔四面。周旋右轉書五字陀羅
<lb n="0705c04" ed="T"/>尼。遶塔行道念誦勿令斷絕。滿五<note n="0705028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">落＝洛【三】【甲】</note><note n="0705028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">落＝洛【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0705028"><lem wit="【大】">落</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">洛</rdg></app>叉遍。</p>
<lb n="0705c05" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0705c0501">爾時如來及文殊師利執金剛等。於虛空中
<lb n="0705c06" ed="T"/>而<app source="0705018" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">現</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">見</rdg></app>其身<note n="0705029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">仍＝乃【甲】</note><app n="0705029"><lem wit="【大】">仍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">乃</rdg></app>為說法。</p></div1>
<lb n="0705c07" ed="T"/><div1 type="pin"><mulu level="1" n="2" label="金剛頂經瑜伽文殊師利菩薩儀軌供養法品" type="品"/><head>金剛頂<note n="0705030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經瑜伽＝瑜伽經【乙】</note><app n="0705030"><lem wit="【大】">經瑜伽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">瑜伽經</rdg></app>文殊師利菩薩<note n="0705031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔儀軌供養〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0705031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔儀軌供養〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0705031"><lem wit="【大】">儀軌供養</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>法
<lb n="0705c08" ed="T"/><note n="0705032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一品〕－【乙】</note><app n="0705032"><lem wit="【大】">一品</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0705033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此下甲本奧書曰，貞享四丁卯年正月二十七日一校加點了淨嚴四十九載，元祿十六年正月十八日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教</note></head>
<lb n="0705c09" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0705c0901"><l><note n="0705034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自此以下至卷末宋元明三本及甲本俱無之 cf. No. 1175</note>歸命童真妙吉祥</l><l>我依瑜伽說念誦</l>
<lb n="0705c10" ed="T"/><l>身口意業金剛念</l><l>如來甚深三密門</l>
<lb n="0705c11" ed="T"/><l>行者應發普賢心</l><l>從師應受金剛戒</l>
<lb n="0705c12" ed="T"/><l>不顧身命起慈悲</l><l>方可堪入解脫輪</l>
<lb n="0705c13" ed="T"/><l>應從師受三麼耶</l><l>契印密語如經說</l>
<lb n="0705c14" ed="T"/><l>敬阿闍梨如佛想</l><l>於同學所慇重心</l>
<lb n="0705c15" ed="T"/><l>或於山間阿蘭若</l><l>流泉浴池悅意樹</l>
<lb n="0705c16" ed="T"/><l>山&CB00123;石窟&CB00529;樹<note n="0705035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">邊＝間【乙】</note><app n="0705035"><lem wit="【大】">邊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">間</rdg></app></l><l>建立壇場如本法</l>
<lb n="0705c17" ed="T"/><l>莊嚴精室置本尊</l><l>隨力供養一心住</l>
<lb n="0705c18" ed="T"/><l>遍觀十方諸佛海</l><l>供養禮諸如來足</l>
<lb n="0705c19" ed="T"/><l>為成三業金剛故</l><l>當於二手舌心中</l>
<lb n="0705c20" ed="T"/><l>應想五智金剛杵</l><l><note n="0705036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">由此＝猶如【乙】</note><app n="0705036"><lem wit="【大】">由此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">猶如</rdg></app>加持皆悉地</l>
<lb n="0705c21" ed="T"/><l>次應結契名警覺</l><l>二<note n="0705037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">手＝中【乙】</note><app n="0705037"><lem wit="【大】">手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">中</rdg></app>皆作金剛拳</l>
<lb n="0705c22" ed="T"/><l>檀慧相鉤&CB00594;進力</l><l>二度側<note n="0705038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拄＝柱【乙】</note><app n="0705038"><lem wit="【大】">拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">柱</rdg></app>成覺悟</l></lg>
<lb n="0705c23" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0705c2301">警覺真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0705c24" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0705c2401" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日<note n="0705039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝嚧【乙】</note><app n="0705039"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">嚧</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
