<lb n="0706c03" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0706c0301"><l>次結文殊三麼耶</l><l>十度相叉成滿月</l>
<lb n="0706c04" ed="T"/><l><note n="0706019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">直申＝真身【乙】</note><app n="0706019"><lem wit="【大】">直申</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">真身</rdg></app>忍願金剛劍</l><l>想身同等妙吉祥</l></lg>
<lb n="0706c05" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0706c0501">三麼<note n="0706020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔耶〕－【乙】</note><app n="0706020"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0706c06" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0706c0601" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note place="inline">丁以反引</note>乞叉儜<note place="inline">三合</note>三麼耶娑怛
<lb n="0706c07" ed="T"/>&CB00680;<note place="inline"><note n="0706021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝三【乙】</note><app n="0706021"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">三</rdg></app>合</note></p>
<lb n="0706c08" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0706c0801"><l>次<note n="0706022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">當結＝結極【乙】</note><app n="0706022"><lem wit="【大】">當結</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">結極</rdg></app>喜三昧印</l><l>定慧為月堅固縛</l>
<lb n="0706c09" ed="T"/><l>忍辱願度中交合</l><l>檀慧禪智&CB00594;相著</l></lg>
<lb n="0706c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0706c1001">真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0706c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0706c1101" type="dharani"><note n="0706023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">奄＝唵【乙】＊</note><app n="0706023"><lem wit="【大】">奄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">唵</rdg></app>三麼耶穀<note place="inline">引</note>蘇囉多娑怛&CB00680;<note place="inline">三合</note></p>
<lb n="0706c12" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0706c1201"><l>次結金剛降三世</l><l>想身同彼無差別</l>
<lb n="0706c13" ed="T"/><l>止觀二羽金剛拳</l><l>檀慧相<note n="0706024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鉤＝釣【乙】</note><app n="0706024"><lem wit="【大】">鉤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">釣</rdg></app>&CB00594;進力</l>
<lb n="0706c14" ed="T"/><l>左轉辟除右結界</l><l>悲心示現威怒形</l></lg>
<lb n="0706c15" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0706c1501">降三世真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0706c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0706c1601" type="dharani">唵遜<note n="0706025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婆＋（去）細註【乙】</note><app n="0706025"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">婆<note place="inline">去</note></rdg></app>&CB00135;遜婆<note n="0706026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔&CB00135;〕－【乙】</note><app n="0706026"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00135;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app><note place="inline">去</note>吽<note place="inline">短</note>仡哩<note place="inline">二合</note>釁<note n="0706027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔拏〕－【乙】</note><app n="0706027"><lem wit="【大】">拏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二
<lb n="0706c17" ed="T"/>合</note><note n="0706028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吃＝仡【乙】</note><app n="0706028"><lem wit="【大】">吃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">仡</rdg></app>哩<note place="inline">二合</note>釁拏<note place="inline">二合</note>吽<note place="inline">短</note>仡哩<note place="inline">二合</note>釁拏<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0706c18" ed="T"/>跛耶吽<note place="inline">短</note>阿囊耶斛<note place="inline">引</note>婆&CB00344;&CB00680;&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>吽<note place="inline">短</note>
<lb n="0706c19" ed="T"/>泮吒<note place="inline">半音</note></p>
<lb n="0706c20" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0706c2001"><l>次結蓮花三麼耶</l><l>為令觀行成就故</l>
<lb n="0706c21" ed="T"/><l>十度相叉作為月</l><l>禪智檀慧&CB00594;相著</l></lg>
<lb n="0706c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0706c2201">真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0706c23" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0706c2301" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>跛娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>三麼耶娑怛&CB00680;<note place="inline">三合</note></p>
<lb n="0706c24" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0706c2401">行者應修阿薩頗那伽法。修此法者。不動支
<lb n="0706c25" ed="T"/>節止出入息。令其微細勿使散亂。即應觀於
<lb n="0706c26" ed="T"/>虛空一切諸佛。由如胡麻遍滿十方。以金剛
<lb n="0706c27" ed="T"/>彈指告行者言。善男子。汝觀本心。行者聞
<lb n="0706c28" ed="T"/><note n="0706029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＝以【乙】</note><app n="0706029"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">以</rdg></app>即想自身禮諸佛足。禮畢諦觀本心白諸
<lb n="0706c29" ed="T"/>佛言。心相無體云何修證。</p>
<pb n="0707a" id="T20.1171.0707a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0707a01" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a0101">諸佛告行者言。善男子。汝觀心中月輪如在
<lb n="0707a02" ed="T"/>輕霧。即誦瑩徹菩提真言。</p>
<lb n="0707a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a0301">諦觀心月真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707a04" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a0401" type="dharani">唵質多&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note place="inline">丁以反</note>吠鄧迦嚕彌</p>
<lb n="0707a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a0501">行者應了了諦觀。不久當見清淨菩提心。離
<lb n="0707a06" ed="T"/>諸塵垢淨如滿月。即誦菩提心真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707a07" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a0701" type="dharani">唵冒地質多母怛跛<note place="inline">二合引</note>那夜<note n="0707001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【乙】</note><app n="0707001"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>彌</p>
<lb n="0707a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a0801">想菩提月中有曇字。如金色輝曜。如日放大
<lb n="0707a09" ed="T"/>光明。便即變成般若波羅蜜劍。離諸分別能
<lb n="0707a10" ed="T"/>斷煩惱。想為智劍真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a1101" type="dharani">唵底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note>渴&CB00344;</p>
<lb n="0707a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a1201">想其智劍漸漸增大遍周法界真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707a13" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a1301" type="dharani">唵娑頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉渴&CB00344;</p>
<lb n="0707a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a1401">想其智劍漸漸收攝等自身量真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a1501" type="dharani">唵僧賀囉渴&CB00344;</p>
<lb n="0707a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a1601">為令智劍堅固不散復誦真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707a17" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a1701" type="dharani">唵涅哩<note place="inline">二合</note>荼底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note>渴&CB00344;</p>
<lb n="0707a18" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a1801">想空中如來盡入智劍同為一體。作是思惟。
<lb n="0707a19" ed="T"/>如彼諸佛體性我亦同然真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707a20" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a2001" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">三</note>麼喻<note place="inline">引</note>含摩訶<note place="inline">引</note>三<note n="0707002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＝麼【乙】＊</note><app n="0707002"><lem wit="【大】">摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">麼</rdg></app>喻<note place="inline">引</note>含薩&CB00085;怛他
<lb n="0707a21" ed="T"/>&CB00617;多鼻<note n="0707003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝三【乙】</note><app n="0707003"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">三</rdg></app><note place="inline">去</note>&CB00155;<note place="inline">引</note>地渴&CB00344;怛麼<note place="inline">二合</note>句<note place="inline">引</note>含</p>
<lb n="0707a22" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a2201">想其智劍漸漸變成文殊師利童真菩薩。具
<lb n="0707a23" ed="T"/>大威德身著種種瓔珞。頂想五髻。右手持智
<lb n="0707a24" ed="T"/>劍。左手執青蓮花。花上<note n="0707004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有〕－【乙】</note><app n="0707004"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>般若波羅蜜經
<lb n="0707a25" ed="T"/>夾。身色如&CB00614;金。心誦阿<note n="0707005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝羅【乙】</note><app n="0707005"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">羅</rdg></app>跛者曩一遍。</p>
<lb n="0707a26" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0707a2601"><l>次結金剛智劍印</l><l>止觀相叉作滿月</l>
<lb n="0707a27" ed="T"/><l>忍願皆&CB00594;如劍形</l><l>印心及<note n="0707006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">額＝顛【乙】</note><app n="0707006"><lem wit="【大】">額</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">顛</rdg></app>喉頂上</l>
<lb n="0707a28" ed="T"/><l>即成護身堅本尊</l></lg>
<lb n="0707a29" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707a2901">真言曰。</p>
<pb n="0707b" id="T20.1171.0707b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0707b01" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707b0101" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底乞叉拏<note place="inline">三合</note>地瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note>娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0707b02" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;</p>
<lb n="0707b03" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0707b0301"><l>次當灌頂結寶印</l><l>二手相叉作為月</l>
<lb n="0707b04" ed="T"/><l>進力反屈如寶形</l><l>禪智二度下相捻</l>
<lb n="0707b05" ed="T"/><l>置於額上分兩邊</l><l>便結智拳如<note n="0707007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">繫＝擊【乙】</note><app n="0707007"><lem wit="【大】">繫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">擊</rdg></app>帛</l>
<lb n="0707b06" ed="T"/><l>兩手向前徐徐散</l><l>當知已繫無垢繒</l></lg>
<lb n="0707b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707b0701">真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707b0801" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>莽&CB00619;鼻曬計囉鼻詵
<lb n="0707b09" ed="T"/>者娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;薩&CB00085;母捺囉<note place="inline">二合</note>冥涅哩<note place="inline">二合</note>雉
<lb n="0707b10" ed="T"/>句嚕&CB00085;囉迦&CB00085;制娜&CB00680;</p>
<lb n="0707b11" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0707b1101"><l>次結寶劍自灌頂</l><l>二手合掌屈進力</l>
<lb n="0707b12" ed="T"/><l>禪智皆屈入掌中</l><l>置於額上分兩邊</l></lg>
<lb n="0707b13" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707b1301">灌頂真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707b14" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707b1401" type="dharani">唵囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>俱舍仡哩耶<note place="inline">三合</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0707b15" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0707b1501"><l>次復結於甲冑印</l><l>二手皆作金剛拳</l>
<lb n="0707b16" ed="T"/><l>置於心前&CB00594;進力</l><l>左右二度想唵砧</l>
<lb n="0707b17" ed="T"/><l>想流清光為綠色</l><l>心前三轉遶背後</l>
<lb n="0707b18" ed="T"/><l>復至臍下及兩膝</l><l>又轉至臍遶腰後</l>
<lb n="0707b19" ed="T"/><l>從腰到心轉兩膊</l><l>從膊至喉向頸後</l>
<lb n="0707b20" ed="T"/><l>復從頸後至額前</l><l>從額至腦結智拳</l>
<lb n="0707b21" ed="T"/><l>徐徐散下如垂帶</l><l><note n="0707008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">上＝止【乙】</note><app n="0707008"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">止</rdg></app>觀旋轉如舞勢</l>
<lb n="0707b22" ed="T"/><l>二手相叉成滿月</l></lg>
<lb n="0707b23" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707b2301">甲冑真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707b24" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707b2401" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>迦&CB00085;左&CB00085;日&CB00074;<note place="inline">二合</note>句嚕&CB00085;日囉
<lb n="0707b25" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0707009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔娜〕－【乙】</note><app n="0707009"><lem wit="【大】">娜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>含</p>
<lb n="0707b26" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0707b2601"><l>次陳金剛拍掌儀</l><l>二羽齊拍<note n="0707010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一＝三【乙】</note><app n="0707010"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">三</rdg></app>相拍</l>
<lb n="0707b27" ed="T"/><l>由陳拍印真言并</l><l>能令聖眾發歡喜</l>
<lb n="0707b28" ed="T"/><l>速獲本尊堅固體</l></lg>
<lb n="0707b29" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707b2901">歡喜真言曰。</p>
<pb n="0707c" id="T20.1171.0707c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0707c01" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707c0101" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note place="inline">引</note>乞叉拏<note place="inline">三合</note>&CB00418;使野<note place="inline">二合</note>斛<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0707c02" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0707c0201"><l>次當行者座前觀</l><l>八葉蓮花具鬚&CB00610;</l>
<lb n="0707c03" ed="T"/><l>上觀師子妙高座</l><l>座上復有七寶樓</l>
<lb n="0707c04" ed="T"/><l>中想七寶蓮花王</l><l>上想曇字具威<note n="0707011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">光＝德【乙】</note><app n="0707011"><lem wit="【大】">光</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">德</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0707c05" ed="T"/><l>遍照法界靡不周</l><l>其字變為金剛利</l>
<lb n="0707c06" ed="T"/><l>了了諦觀如本形</l><l>召請菩薩入想身</l>
<lb n="0707c07" ed="T"/><l>二手作月進如鉤</l><l>想身同於彼菩薩</l></lg>
<lb n="0707c08" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707c0801">金剛鉤菩薩真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707c0901" type="dharani">唵阿夜<note place="inline">引</note>呬弱</p>
<lb n="0707c10" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0707c1001"><l>次當結索入尊身</l><l>結月禪押智入掌</l>
<lb n="0707c11" ed="T"/><l>由此密印加持故</l><l>變為一體無有差</l></lg>
<lb n="0707c12" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707c1201">金剛索真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707c13" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707c1301" type="dharani">唵阿呬吽吽</p>
<lb n="0707c14" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0707c1401"><l>次當鎖印令堅固</l><l>作月四度猶如環</l>
<lb n="0707c15" ed="T"/><l>由此祕印威力故</l><l>悉令堅固而不變</l></lg>
<lb n="0707c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707c1601">金剛鎖真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707c17" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707c1701" type="dharani">唵係娑普<note place="inline">二合</note>吒<note n="0707012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00680;＝&CB00805;【乙】</note><app n="0707012"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00680;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&CB00805;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0707c18" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0707c1801"><l>次結鈴印令歡喜</l><l>禪智八掌如鈴鐸</l>
<lb n="0707c19" ed="T"/><l>令尊及眾皆歡喜</l><l>加持令速妙成就</l></lg>
<lb n="0707c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707c2001">金剛鈴真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707c21" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707c2101" type="dharani">唵健吒噁噁</p>
<lb n="0707c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707c2201">行者次當兩手捧遏伽想洗金剛利菩薩及諸
<lb n="0707c23" ed="T"/>眷屬<note n="0707013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">足＝之【乙】</note><app n="0707013"><lem wit="【大】">足</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">之</rdg></app>。或以百字真言加持遏伽。而獻遏伽
<lb n="0707c24" ed="T"/>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0707c25" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707c2501" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日<note n="0707014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">盧二合＝嚧【乙】</note><app n="0707014"><lem wit="【大】">盧<note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">嚧</rdg></app>娜迦吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0707c26" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0707c2601"><l>次結曼殊羯磨印</l><l>二羽皆作金剛拳</l>
<lb n="0707c27" ed="T"/><l>禪羽置於自心上</l><l>右手猶如執劍勢</l>
<lb n="0707c28" ed="T"/><l>由此羯<app source="0706004" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">麼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">磨</rdg></app>妙印力</l><l>身獲如尊等無異</l></lg>
<lb n="0707c29" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0707c2901">羯<app source="0706004" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">麼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">磨</rdg></app>真言曰。</p>
<pb n="0708a" id="T20.1171.0708a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0708a01" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a0101" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底乞叉拏<note place="inline">三合</note>曇</p>
<lb n="0708a02" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0708a0201"><l>次結金剛利劍印</l><l>結月忍願申如劍</l>
<lb n="0708a03" ed="T"/><l>由此金剛利妙印</l><l>當獲般若甚深智</l></lg>
<lb n="0708a04" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a0401">金剛利真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0708a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a0501" type="dharani">唵耨佉泚娜</p>
<lb n="0708a06" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0708a0601"><l>次復當結內供養</l><l>結月當心&CB00594;禪智</l>
<lb n="0708a07" ed="T"/><l>由結金剛<note n="0708001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嬉＝喜【乙】＊</note><app n="0708001"><lem wit="【大】">嬉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">喜</rdg></app>戲印</l><l>速滿檀那波羅蜜</l></lg>
<lb n="0708a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a0801">金剛<app source="0708001" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">嬉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">喜</rdg></app>戲真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0708a09" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a0901" type="dharani">唵摩訶囉底</p>
<lb n="0708a10" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0708a1001"><l>次結金剛鬘供養</l><l>依前<app source="0708001" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">嬉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">喜</rdg></app>戲直申臂</l>
<lb n="0708a11" ed="T"/><l>由結此印加持故</l><l>當滿淨戒波羅密</l></lg>
<lb n="0708a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a1201">金剛鬘真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0708a13" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a1301" type="dharani">唵嚕跛戍<note place="inline">引</note>鞞</p>
<lb n="0708a14" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0708a1401"><l>次結金剛歌詠印</l><l>鬘至臍口垂下散</l>
<lb n="0708a15" ed="T"/><l>由結金剛歌密印</l><l>速獲安忍波羅蜜</l></lg>
<lb n="0708a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a1601">金剛歌真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0708a17" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a1701" type="dharani">唵戍嚕<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>掃磎</p>
<lb n="0708a18" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0708a1801"><l>次結金剛舞供養</l><l>二手拳旋如舞勢</l>
<lb n="0708a19" ed="T"/><l>由結舞印加持<note n="0708002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">故＝力【乙】</note><app n="0708002"><lem wit="【大】">故</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">力</rdg></app></l><l>速滿精進波羅蜜</l></lg>
<lb n="0708a20" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a2001">金剛舞印真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0708a21" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a2101" type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;布爾</p>
<lb n="0708a22" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0708a2201"><l>次結金剛外供養</l><l>二手作月向下散</l>
<lb n="0708a23" ed="T"/><l>由結燒香印力故</l><l>當證靜慮波羅蜜</l></lg>
<lb n="0708a24" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a2401">金剛燒香真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0708a25" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a2501" type="dharani">唵&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>賀&CB00256;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;<note place="inline">引</note>寧<note place="inline">上</note></p>
<lb n="0708a26" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0708a2601"><l>次結金剛散花印</l><l>結月向上如散花</l>
<lb n="0708a27" ed="T"/><l>由此散花印加持</l><l>速證般若波羅蜜</l></lg>
<lb n="0708a28" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a2801">金剛散花真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0708a29" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708a2901" type="dharani">唵頗&CB00256;<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;銘</p>
<pb n="0708b" id="T20.1171.0708b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0708b01" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0708b0101"><l>次結金剛燈明印</l><l>作月禪智頭相著</l>
<lb n="0708b02" ed="T"/><l>由結金剛燈明印</l><l>當得方便波羅蜜</l></lg>
<lb n="0708b03" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708b0301">金剛燈明真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0708b04" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708b0401" type="dharani"><app source="0706023" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">奄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">唵</rdg></app>蘇帝惹<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00617;哩<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0708b05" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0708b0501"><l>次結金剛塗香印</l><l>月當胸散如塗香</l>
<lb n="0708b06" ed="T"/><l>由結塗香印加持</l><l>速滿誓願波羅蜜</l></lg>
<lb n="0708b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708b0701">金剛塗香真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0708b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708b0801" type="dharani">唵蘇健蕩倪<note place="inline">倪以<note n="0708003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔兮〕－【乙】</note><app n="0708003"><lem wit="【大】">兮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>反</note></p>
<lb n="0708b09" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708b0901">行者次應誦一百八名讚供養本尊。又結金
<lb n="0708b10" ed="T"/>剛利劍印。於心上誦百字真言加持自身。假
<lb n="0708b11" ed="T"/>使過去世中造種種惡業五無間等一切罪
<lb n="0708b12" ed="T"/>障。由此百字真言加持故。一切罪障悉皆消
<lb n="0708b13" ed="T"/>滅。見身獲得首楞嚴三昧。若心散亂數誦此
<lb n="0708b14" ed="T"/>明或一七三七乃至七七一百八遍。心離攀
<lb n="0708b15" ed="T"/>緣速得三摩地。</p>
<lb n="0708b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708b1601">百字真言</p>
<lb n="0708b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708b1701" type="dharani">唵渴&CB00344;薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合一</note>三麼耶麼努播<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00256;耶<note place="inline"><note n="0708004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合〕－【乙】</note><app n="0708004"><lem wit="【大】">二合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0708b18" ed="T"/>二</note>渴&CB00344;薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline"><note n="0708005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二合三＝三二合【乙】</note><app n="0708005"><lem wit="【大】">二合三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">三二合</rdg></app></note>底吠<note place="inline">二合</note>怒跛底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合四</note>
<lb n="0708b19" ed="T"/>涅哩<note place="inline">二合</note>住<note place="inline"><note n="0708006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">茶＝荼【乙】</note><app n="0708006"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">荼</rdg></app>護反</note>銘婆<note place="inline"><note n="0708007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">去＝上【乙】</note><app n="0708007"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">上</rdg></app></note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">五</note>素&CB00418;使喻<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0708b20" ed="T"/>銘婆<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">六</note>阿<note place="inline">上</note><note n="0708008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拏＝努【乙】</note><app n="0708008"><lem wit="【大】">拏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">努</rdg></app>囉訖&CB00418;<note place="inline">二合</note>銘婆<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">七</note>素
<lb n="0708b21" ed="T"/>布使喻<note place="inline">二合引</note>銘婆<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">八</note>薩&CB00085;悉朕<note place="inline">提飲反</note>銘&CB00425;囉
<lb n="0708b22" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>也瑳<note place="inline">九</note>薩&CB00085;羯磨素者銘<note place="inline">十</note>質多失唎<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0708b23" ed="T"/>藥句嚕<note place="inline">十一</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note>訶訶訶訶斛<note place="inline">引</note>婆&CB00344;&CB00680;<note place="inline">十二</note>薩
<lb n="0708b24" ed="T"/>&CB00085;怛他&CB00617;多<note place="inline">十三</note>渴&CB00344;麼銘門<note place="inline">上</note>者<note n="0708009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔十四〕－【乙】</note><app n="0708009"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">十四</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>渴倪
<lb n="0708b25" ed="T"/><note place="inline">倪以反</note>婆&CB00085;<note place="inline">十五</note><app source="0707002" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">麼</rdg></app>訶三摩耶薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>惡<note place="inline">引十六</note></p>
<lb n="0708b26" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708b2601">不散前印。諦觀前有本尊。及想自身如本尊
<lb n="0708b27" ed="T"/>無異。了了諦觀即誦五字陀羅尼。或以金剛
<lb n="0708b28" ed="T"/>語誦。<note n="0708010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">或＝我【乙】</note><app n="0708010"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">我</rdg></app>分明蓮華語誦。或誦七遍三七遍。
<lb n="0708b29" ed="T"/>以印於頂上解散。次即把念珠當心念誦不
<pb n="0708c" id="T20.1171.0708c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0708c01" ed="T"/>緩不急。或一百八遍或一千乃至一萬遍。念
<lb n="0708c02" ed="T"/>誦數畢。二手<note n="0708011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捧＝棒【乙】</note><app n="0708011"><lem wit="【大】">捧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">棒</rdg></app>珠安於頂上。然後置本處。
<lb n="0708c03" ed="T"/>若三摩地念誦者。當心觀大圓鏡智。中布
<lb n="0708c04" ed="T"/>五字門。了了諦觀。隨義相應。心與般若波羅
<lb n="0708c05" ed="T"/>蜜合。此名三摩地念誦。若身疲懈。即結本尊
<lb n="0708c06" ed="T"/>劍印。誦五字陀羅尼七遍。復以八大供養供
<lb n="0708c07" ed="T"/>養諸佛。以妙音辭稱揚讚歎。獻閼伽水。以降
<lb n="0708c08" ed="T"/>三世印左旋解界。即結金剛利劍印。奉送諸
<lb n="0708c09" ed="T"/>聖。各還本宮。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0708c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708c1001" type="dharani">唵訖哩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00418;<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">無莫反一</note>薩&CB00085;薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉他
<lb n="0708c11" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合二</note>悉地捺多<note place="inline">引三</note>也他<note place="inline">引</note>努&CB00344;<note place="inline"><note n="0708012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引上四＝上四引【乙】</note><app n="0708012"><lem wit="【大】">引上四</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">上四引</rdg></app></note>&CB00617;縒<note n="0708013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">持＝特【乙】</note><app n="0708013"><lem wit="【大】">持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">特</rdg></app>
<lb n="0708c12" ed="T"/>挽<note place="inline">二合</note>沒馱尾灑焰<note place="inline">五</note>布曩囉<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;<note place="inline">六</note>麼囊<note place="inline">引</note>也
<lb n="0708c13" ed="T"/>都<note place="inline">七</note>唵渴&CB00344;薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>目<note place="inline">八</note></p>
<lb n="0708c14" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708c1401">作此法已。重以三麼耶印誦加持明以印四
<lb n="0708c15" ed="T"/>處。然後灌頂。被金<note n="0708014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔剛〕－【乙】</note><app n="0708014"><lem wit="【大】">剛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>甲冑。依前四禮禮四
<lb n="0708c16" ed="T"/>方佛。懺悔發願等。然後依閑靜處。嚴以香花
<lb n="0708c17" ed="T"/>住本尊三摩地。讀誦方廣一切大乘經典大
<lb n="0708c18" ed="T"/>般若大品。乃至文殊般若等。隨意經行。</p>
<lb n="0708c19" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0708c1901"><l>若有智者依<note n="0708015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此＋（教）【乙】</note><app n="0708015"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">此教</rdg></app>法</l><l>晝夜四時精進修</l>
<lb n="0708c20" ed="T"/><l><note n="0708016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">見＝現【乙】</note><app n="0708016"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">現</rdg></app>世證得歡喜地</l><l>後十六生成正覺</l></lg>
<lb n="0708c21" ed="T"/><note n="0708017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔文殊…二合〕百二十九字－【乙】</note><app word-count="129" n="0708017"><lem wit="【大】"><p id="pT20p0708c2101">文殊師利忿怒陀羅尼</p>
<lb n="0708c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708c2201" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底乞叉拏<note place="inline">三合</note>俱嚕<note place="inline">二合</note>馱瞋那
<lb n="0708c23" ed="T"/>瞋那吽<note place="inline">引</note>泮吒</p>
<lb n="0708c24" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708c2401">用此真言護身辟除結界。淨諸香花及一切
<lb n="0708c25" ed="T"/>供具等並得。</p>
<lb n="0708c26" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT20p0708c2601"><l>當願眾生遇此教</l><l>曼殊常為善知識</l>
<lb n="0708c27" ed="T"/><l>速證般若善巧智</l><l>疾成無上兩足尊</l></lg>
<lb n="0708c28" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708c2801">五字陀羅尼</p>
<lb n="0708c29" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0708c2901" type="dharani">阿囉跛者曩唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底乞叉拏<note place="inline">三合</note>唵耨
<pb n="0709a" id="T20.1171.0709a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0709a01" ed="T"/>佉泚<note place="inline">去</note>娜唵渴&CB00344;&CB00617;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>欠<note place="inline">平</note>唵渴&CB00344;薩怛
<lb n="0709a02" ed="T"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note></p></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0709a03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>金剛頂經瑜伽文殊師利菩薩法<note n="0709001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一品＝品一卷【乙】</note><app n="0709001"><lem wit="【大】">一品</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">品一卷</rdg></app></jhead></juan></div1>
